      .container
        .row
          .col-md-12
            h1 Things to be aware of
            h5 If you ever encounter a problem with the Program Of Study please check that you have adequate placeholders. Placeholders allow for the program of study to be viewable when information is unavailable. Such as a student has a course where there is no pre-requisites. The program works because a placeholder is shown in the pre-requisites box. If there was no pre-requisite then the program would not be able to display wihtout a course having all fields.
        .row
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 5%;')
            img(src='/assets/POS/changeadvisor.png', alt='Picture Not Found', width='100%', height='100%')
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 5%;')
            h1 Change Advisor
            h5 To change a students advisor. Find the folllowing box. Double click on empty input to display all avaiable advisors in the system.
        .row
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 10%;')
            img(src='/assets/POS/changecatalog.png', alt='Picture Not Found', width='70%', height='70%')
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 10%;')
            h1 Change Catalog
            h5 To see how a students current courses line up with an existing catalog click on the catalog button to choose from the list of available catalogs.
        .row
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 10%;')
            img(src='/assets/POS/gpadate.png', alt='Picture Not Found', width='100%', height='100%')
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 12%;')
            h1 GPA & Date
            h5 The system will automatically calculate the students GPA based on grades and credit hours listed in the Program Of Study. The Meeting date will automatically generate to the current date and archive the report based on this date.
        .row
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 12%;')
            img(src='/assets/POS/pos_download.png', alt='Picture Not Found', width='50%', height='50%')
            img(src='/assets/POS/pos_submit.png', alt='Picture Not Found', width='50%', height='50%')
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 10%;')
            h1 Download & Submit
            h5 Clicking download will generate a CSV file with all of the students data. Clicking submit will update advisor, semester, grade, course codes; in the system. It will also create a CSV that will be saved into the system and displayed on the archive page for each student. CSV's will be stored based on date and time to the minute.
        .row
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 12%;')
            img(src='/assets/POS/pos_semgradecodename.png', alt='Picture Not Found ', width='100%', height='90%')
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 12%;')
            h1 Semester, Grade, Code, & Name
            h5 Semester and Grade have drop down boxes for all approved values. Course Code, when empty, can be double clicked to show all avaiable courses. Entering or Changing any of these values will update them when you press submit. The course name will not be updated and can be clicked for an expanded view.
        .row
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 10%;')
            img(src='/assets/POS/pos_as.png', alt='Picture Not Found', width='100%', height='90%')
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 10%;')
            h1 Advanced Standing
            h5 Advanced Standing can be checked off and the color will change from red to green. When checked you can click submit and the check will stay saved with the student. Hovering over the text will show the requirements for Advanced Standing.
        
        .row
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 10%;')
            img(src='/assets/POS/pos_heading.png', alt='Picture Not Found', width='80%', height='80%')
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 14%;')
            h1 Headings
            h5 Headings are matched to courses to display the correct order. These can be changed in the 'Edit Layout' pages.

